title: Championship Manager 1 (1993) Updated to season 2012-2013
description:
Ever wanted to play the original Championship Manager,only with more updated database? Well here is the Championship Manager 93 Edition,updated with 2012-2013 data. Players like Christiano Ronaldo,Neymar++ are all available.

There ARE bugs,and the fact that its build on the rather crappy CM93 version,this may not be for you. It would been better to build it on the CM94EOS version imho.

Thank you for seeding!
